# Navigation

## Bottom Toolbar

The toolbar uses Material Design 3 navigation bar component.
Icons use Material Symbols (Outlined style):

- Tasks: `checklist`
- Lists: `view_list`
- Settings: `settings`

The active item uses a filled icon with a tinted indicator pill behind it.

@ref(https://m3.material.io/components/navigation-bar)

## Screen Transitions

Navigation transitions use Material Motion shared-axis pattern (horizontal)
for top-level destinations and container-transform for detail views.
The system back button and predictive back gesture are fully supported.

@ref(https://m3.material.io/styles/motion/transitions/transition-patterns)
